  "info": {
    "title": "Aspose.PSD Crop CLI App for .NET",
    "version": "24.6.0",
    "description": "Aspose.PSD Crop CLI App for .NET provides crop functionality for PSD, PSB and AI file formats without requiring Adobe Photoshop or Adobe Illustrator. It supports cropping by rectangle or circle. The result of cropping can be exported to one of the supported formats including PSD, PSB, PNG, JPEG, PDF, TIFF, GIF, BMP, JPEG2000. PSD CLI Crop App supports quick and pixel-perfect (in the most cases) exporting of cropped data. It can be used as standalone console application on the any platform that supports .NET including Windows, MacOS, MacOS-Arm, Linux. This App is frequently used for business process automation."
  },
